  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"Join our discord if you have issues\" href=\"https://discord.gg/AsFE4T9FbN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/luWUDcU.png\" alt=\"Write in discord if you have issues\" width=\"100\" height=\"38\" /></a>&nbsp;<a title=\"CurseForge Page\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/B8ZRmEo.png\" alt=\"CurseForge page\" width=\"131\" height=\"38\" /></a>&nbsp;<a title=\"You want support me?\" href=\"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=NN9AT4W75FD5S\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/gxtfQds.png\" width=\"95\" height=\"38\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8ndKits.png\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" alt=\"Just Leveling\" /> <img src=\"https://imgur.com/Vsaw6BJ.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"245\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8ndKits.png\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/3DD4Udv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"222\" height=\"40\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9990\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/trXUtrT.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"42\" height=\"24\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9971\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/HY4nys2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"24\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9776\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/zmDeGXO.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"43\" height=\"24\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9550\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/f4ftbOl.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"43\" height=\"24\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9366\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/bcfGV52.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"43\" height=\"24\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9259\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/cVR4nMN.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"42\" height=\"24\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9186\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/mpRSLIH.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"34\" height=\"24\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-leveling/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A9008\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/Mrq8sjJ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"43\" height=\"24\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8ndKits.png\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Just Leveling is a RPG inspired on <a title=\"Reskillable\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/reskillable\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Reskillable mod</a>, now you have passives and skills, passives can upgrade to level 0 to 10, skills can enabled or disabled depending the level required, like reskillable the items have requirements and finally for the titles also have requirements, you can put it on you nameplate. Discover all skills and try to unlock all titles if you can.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you wanna learn about Passives/Skills/Titles go to the <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Leveling/wiki/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wiki</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">New compat with <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-combat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BetterCombat</a>:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">New compat with <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cloth Config</a>:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/1sm58Vc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"377\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8ndKits.png\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/cOWQghI.gif\" width=\"412\" height=\"233\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://imgur.com/TkSjYie.gif\" width=\"412\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/SAFKa6h.png\" width=\"412\" height=\"233\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://imgur.com/w5u3rgN.gif\" width=\"412\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/J0FQSK3.png\" width=\"412\" height=\"234\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://imgur.com/AX5Xe1D.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"412\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8ndKits.png\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>F.A.Q.s</strong></span></em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: Can i include Just Leveling in my mod pack?</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A: Sure, just put my mod in the related projects</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: Can i add more Skills / Titles?</strong><br />A: Yes you can, see the <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Leveling/wiki/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wiki</a> and learn how to put it</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: How can i open the leveling screen?</strong><br />A: Just press Y, there you can see the skills and change your title</span></p>",
